H(u)=:\overrightarrow{a}+(\overrightarrow{b}-\overrightarrow{a})*u-\overrightarrow{x}+\overrightarrow{v}
\int\limits_{u_0}^{u_1} \exp\left[-\angle(H(u),N)^2\right]du
\overrightarrow{a},\overrightarrow{b},\overrightarrow{x}\in\mathbb{R}^3
\angle(\overrightarrow{u},\overrightarrow{v}):=\cos^{-1}\left(\frac{\overrightarrow{u}\cdot \overrightarrow{v}}{\|\overrightarrow{u}\|\;\|\overrightarrow{v}\|}\right)
H(u)=\left(\begin{smallmatrix}0\\0\\u*\alpha\end{smallmatrix}\right)
\overrightarrow{b}-\overrightarrow{a}=\left(\begin{smallmatrix}0\\0\\u*\beta\end{smallmatrix}\right)
\int e^{-cos^{-1}(x^2)}dx
\int e^{-cos^{-1}(x)}dx
